OL,3,CInflation-busting rise for Tube and
OL,4,Ctrain fares as Sadiq Khan scraps freeze
OL,6,FMillions of Londoners are to be hit
OL,7,Fwith an inflation-busting increase in
OL,8,Fthe cost of their daily commute after
OL,9,FSadiq Khan was forced to scrap his
OL,10,Ffares freeze.
OL,12,FTube and train fares in the capital
OL,13,Fwill rise by 4.6% in March after
OL,14,Fministers ordered the mayor to
OL,15,Fincrease ticket prices in line with
OL,16,Fthe national rail network.
OL,18,FBut bus and tram fares will be frozen.
OL,19,FThe cost of a bus ticket - including
OL,20,Fthe multiple journey 'Hopper' fare -
OL,21,Fwill stay at #1.75.
