OL,3,CInflation-busting rise for Tube and
OL,4,Ctrain fares as Sadiq Khan scraps freeze
OL,6,FCity Hall said buses were the 'most
OL,7,Fused' form of public transport in the
OL,8,Fcapital with 95% of Londoners living
OL,9,Fwithin 400m of a bus stop.
OL,11,FTransport for London was told to match
OL,12,Fthe train companies' fares hike in
OL,13,Freturn for a #485m funding package
OL,14,Fannounced in the budget.
