OL,3,CInflation-busting rise for Tube and
OL,4,Ctrain fares as Sadiq Khan scraps freeze
OL,6,FSadiq Khan said: "Following the
OL,7,FGovernment's budget, ministers made
OL,8,Fclear that to secure national funding
OL,9,Ffor key transport projects in the
OL,10,Ffuture, TfL Tube and rail fares would
OL,11,Fneed to increase in line with national
OL,12,Frail fares.
OL,14,FHe added: "Vital national government
OL,15,Ffunding will allow us to progress
OL,16,Fexciting future projects, such as
OL,17,FSuperloop 2 and more upgrades to the
OL,18,FTube network, as we continue building
OL,19,Fa fairer, safer and greener London for
OL,20,Feveryone.'
